<title>Standards</title>
<para id="fs-idm242495088"><emphasis effect="bold">Topic</emphasis>: 4.2 The Rise of Political Parties and the Era of Jefferson</para>
<para id="fs-idm252566576"><emphasis effect="bold">Theme</emphasis>: PCE Politics and Power</para>
<para id="fs-idm245399568"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Objective</emphasis>: Unit 4B Explain the causes and effects of policy debates in the early republic</para>
<para id="fs-idm241971376"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Development</emphasis>: 4.1.I.B</para>
<para id="fs-idm251534640"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Reasoning Skills</emphasis>: HTS-1 Developments and Processes, HTS-2 Sourcing and Situation, HTS-3 Source Claims and Evidence, HTS-4 Contextualization, HTS-5 Making Connections, HTS-6 Argumentation</para>
